title: Sumadhvavijayaḥ
by_statement: Nārāyaṇapaṇḍitācāryaviracitaḥ ; Nārāyaṇapaṇḍitācāryaviracitabhāvaprakāśikā, Viśvapatitīrthaviracitapadārthadīpikodbodhikā, Chalārīśeṣācāryaviracitamandopakāriṇī iti vyākhyānatrayasametaḥ ; edited by A.B. Shyamachar and S.R. Pandurangi.
publishers: Dvaita Vedanta Studies and Research Foundation

description.value: Verse work on Madhva, 13th cent. Vaishnava religious leader and exponent of dualistic philosophy; includes autocommentary and two classical commentaries.

notes.value:
